-- Rockhopper Shares Slump by 25% in London Trading on Resource Report Delay
-- B y   S t e p h e n   C u n n i n g h a m
-- 2010-10-13T07:11:50Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-10-13/rockhopper-shares-slump-by-25-in-london-trading-on-resource-report-delay.html
Rockhopper Exploration Plc slumped
25 percent in London trading after delaying plans to release a
resource evaluation report because of a disagreement with
consultants over the size of its estimated oil resources off the
Falkland Islands.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
